&oe=66F7D16B"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot3.png", "id": "400523685352869", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974515_400523692019535_8401549706537711147_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WpjR7l9aJnwQ7kNvgFo7SCj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYARd553IpmGPLKUdUenhFCDk-9eeSEYi_DtBtFoBj4H8Q&oe=66F7EEA9"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot4.png", "id": "1301425357334121", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982678_1301425360667454_2162183305064303310_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bQtQnQrQmnQQ7kNvgFlRM9g&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAu3jsXqUjXmtRJrSFRtJuNvQWALwPPx2mAvsREc5X17Q&oe=66F7F522"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverLandscape.png", "id": "443437561075004", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75580070_443437564408337_6207399824729004018_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GK-kc4Lnts0Q7kNvgEkXjJy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBWlI_i2_0dPk80OLTERJ7SmXkPdoewFhP1dY7TTVj9Rw&oe=66F7D497"}, "display_name": "3D scan of the Verdon's canyon", "keywords": ["photogrammetry", "reconstruction", "360camera", "digitization", "scan"], "long_description": "Move like a kayaker in the canyon of the Verdon, reconstructed from videos taken by a helmet-held 360 camera, whose trajectory is about 2.5km long.\n\nRight controller:\n- Rotate on the left or right by using the joystick\n- Update the vertical offset (up or down) by using the joystick\n- Choose a location and teleport to it by using the virtual laser pointer\n- Teleport by using the index trigger only if the laser is green (not red)\n\nLeft controller:\n- Move continuously by using the joystick\n- Switch pannel and map by using the grip/hand trigger\n- If both map and pannel are disabled, switch between rendering modes (texturing or normal colors) by pressing the index trigger\n- The map shows the cloud of mesh vertices and the user location\n- If the pannel is enabled, switch 